---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Pricing — Payerset | Healthcare Price Transparency for Hospitals & Health Systems"
  description="Price transparency and claims data built for hospital finance teams. One platform, every contracted rate in your market."
>

  <!-- ── HERO ── -->
  <section class="relative bg-brand-dark-deep overflow-hidden text-center px-6 pt-20 pb-16">
    <div class="absolute top-[-200px] right-[-100px] w-[700px] h-[700px] rounded-full bg-[radial-gradient(circle,rgba(0,146,202,0.15)_0%,transparent_65%)] pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-[-150px] left-[-80px] w-[500px] h-[500px] rounded-full bg-[radial-gradient(circle,rgba(0,146,202,0.06)_0%,transparent_65%)] pointer-events-none"></div>

    <div class="relative max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-semibold text-white leading-tight tracking-tight mb-3">
        Price Transparency Deserves<br />
        <span class="text-brand-primary">Transparent Pricing.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-white/60 max-w-xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Understand every contracted rate in your market.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── PRODUCT SELECTOR ── -->
  <section class="bg-slate-50 border-y border-slate-200/60 py-10">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <p class="text-center text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[2px] text-slate-400 mb-6">Choose your product</p>
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Rate Explorer -->
      <a href="#rate-explorer-pricing" class="group relative bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-8 text-center shadow-sm hover:border-brand-primary/40 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-brand-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-primary mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 3v11.25A2.25 2.25 0 006 16.5h2.25M3.75 3h-1.5m1.5 0h16.5m0 0h1.5m-1.5 0v11.25A2.25 2.25 0 0118 16.5h-2.25m-7.5 0h7.5m-7.5 0l-1 3m8.5-3l1 3m0 0l.5 1.5m-.5-1.5h-9.5m0 0l-.5 1.5M9 11.25v1.5M12 9v3.75m3-6v6" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Rate Explorer™</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed mb-4">Self-service rate intelligence platform to understand every reimbursement rate.</p>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm font-semibold text-brand-primary group-hover:gap-2.5 transition-all">
          View pricing tiers
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-y-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
          </svg>
        </span>
      </a>

      <!-- Data Lake -->
      <a href="#data-lake-pricing" class="group relative bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-8 text-center shadow-sm hover:border-brand-dark/40 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-brand-dark/10 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-dark mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M20.25 6.375c0 2.278-3.694 4.125-8.25 4.125S3.75 8.653 3.75 6.375m16.5 0c0-2.278-3.694-4.125-8.25-4.125S3.75 4.097 3.75 6.375m16.5 0v11.25c0 2.278-3.694 4.125-8.25 4.125s-8.25-1.847-8.25-4.125V6.375m16.5 0v3.75m-16.5-3.75v3.75m16.5 0v3.75C20.25 16.153 16.556 18 12 18s-8.25-1.847-8.25-4.125v-3.75m16.5 0c0 2.278-3.694 4.125-8.25 4.125s-8.25-1.847-8.25-4.125" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Data Lake™</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed mb-4">Curated transparency data delivered directly to you to power your solutions.</p>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm font-semibold text-brand-dark group-hover:gap-2.5 transition-all">
          View data plans
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-y-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
          </svg>
        </span>
      </a>
    </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── RATE EXPLORER PRICING TABLE ── -->
  <section id="rate-explorer-pricing" class="relative z-10 bg-slate-50/70 border-y border-slate-100 pt-16 pb-16 scroll-mt-8">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-8">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-brand-primary/10 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 mb-4">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 3v11.25A2.25 2.25 0 006 16.5h2.25M3.75 3h-1.5m1.5 0h16.5m0 0h1.5m-1.5 0v11.25A2.25 2.25 0 0118 16.5h-2.25m-7.5 0h7.5m-7.5 0l-1 3m8.5-3l1 3m0 0l.5 1.5m-.5-1.5h-9.5m0 0l-.5 1.5M9 11.25v1.5M12 9v3.75m3-6v6" />
        </svg>
        <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[2px] text-brand-primary">Rate Explorer™</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-slate-900 tracking-tight mb-3">Price Intelligence Platform</h2>
      <p class="text-base text-slate-500 max-w-lg mx-auto">Simple, transparent tiers for hospitals and health systems.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
      <!-- Header row -->
      <div class="hidden sm:grid grid-cols-[1fr_auto_auto] items-center gap-4 px-8 py-4 bg-slate-50 border-b border-slate-200">
        <span class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[1.5px] text-slate-400">Organization Size</span>
        <span class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[1.5px] text-slate-400 text-right w-32">Annual Rate</span>
        <span class="w-32"></span>
      </div>

      {[
        { tier: 'Tier 1', beds: '300 – 999 Beds', desc: 'Multi-facility organizations', price: '95', label: 'K/yr', pricePrefix: null, cta: 'Get Started', ctaStyle: 'bg-brand-primary hover:bg-brand-primary-hover text-white shadow-[0_2px_8px_rgba(0,146,202,0.3)]' },
        { tier: 'Tier 2', beds: '1,000 – 2,999 Beds', desc: 'Regional health systems', price: '195', label: 'K/yr', pricePrefix: null, cta: 'Get Started', ctaStyle: 'bg-brand-primary hover:bg-brand-primary-hover text-white shadow-[0_2px_8px_rgba(0,146,202,0.3)]' },
        { tier: 'Tier 3', beds: '3,000+ Beds', desc: 'Large national health systems', price: '350', label: 'K+/yr', pricePrefix: 'Starting At', cta: 'Talk to Sales', ctaStyle: 'bg-brand-dark hover:bg-brand-dark-deeper text-white shadow-[0_2px_8px_rgba(0,31,41,0.2)]' },
      ].map(({ tier, beds, desc, price, label, pricePrefix, cta, ctaStyle }, i) => (
        <div class:list={[
          "sm:grid grid-cols-[1fr_auto_auto] items-center gap-4 px-8 py-5 transition-colors hover:bg-slate-50/80",
          i < 2 ? "border-b border-slate-100" : "",
        ]}>
          <div class="mb-3 sm:mb-0">
            <p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[2px] text-slate-400 mb-0.5">{tier}</p>
            <p class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 leading-tight">{beds}</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">{desc}</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col items-end font-heading w-32 mb-3 sm:mb-0">
            {pricePrefix && (
              <span class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[1.5px] text-slate-400 mb-0.5">{pricePrefix}</span>
            )}
            <div class="flex items-baseline">
              <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 self-start pt-1">$</span>
              <span class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-none tracking-tight">{price}</span>
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500 ml-0.5">{label}</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a href="/get-started" class:list={["block w-32 text-center px-4 py-3 rounded-lg text-sm font-semibold transition-colors", ctaStyle]}>
            {cta}
          </a>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
    <!-- ── NOT A HEALTH SYSTEM LINK ── -->
    <div class="flex justify-center mt-6">
      <a href="#other-organizations" class="group inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-full pl-5 pr-4 py-3 hover:border-brand-primary/40 hover:bg-brand-primary/5 transition-all duration-200">
        <span class="text-sm text-slate-600">
          <strong class="font-semibold text-slate-800">Not a health system?</strong> We work with consulting firms, med device, health tech, and more.
        </span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-sm font-semibold text-brand-primary whitespace-nowrap shrink-0">
          Learn more
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-y-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
          </svg>
        </span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- ── EVERY PLAN INCLUDES ── -->
    <div class="mt-16">
    <div class="text-center mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-slate-900 tracking-tight">Every Rate Explorer Plan Includes</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
      {[
        {
          title: 'Every Payer & Hospital MRF',
          desc: '100% of published machine-readable files ingested, enriched, and standardized. No subsets, no cherry-picking.',
          icon: `<path d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/>`,
        },
        {
          title: 'Claims & Remits',
          desc: 'See what was actually paid — not just contracted. Real-world claims linked to negotiated rates surface the full picture.',
          icon: `<path d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/>`,
        },
        {
          title: 'Historical Trending',
          desc: 'Full historical data for every payer, hospital, and claims dataset. Track reimbursement movement over time.',
          icon: `<path d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"/>`,
        },
        {
          title: 'Always Human Support',
          desc: 'We work hand-in-hand with your team from day one — answering questions, helping you understand the data, and making sure you get value fast.',
          icon: `<path d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/>`,
        },
        {
          title: 'Quarterly Refreshes',
          desc: 'Full dataset audit and refresh every quarter. Always current with the latest payer structures and CMS requirements.',
          icon: `<path d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15"/>`,
        },
        {
          title: 'Data Engineering Help Built In',
          desc: 'Custom data queries and on-hand help with analysis. Our team works alongside yours to get the answers you need.',
          icon: `<path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/>`,
        },
      ].map(({ title, desc, icon }) => (
        <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-brand-primary hover:shadow-[0_4px_12px_rgba(0,146,202,0.08)] transition-all">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-brand-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-primary mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" set:html={icon} />
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1.5">{title}</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">{desc}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
  </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── DATA LAKE PRICING ── -->
  <section id="data-lake-pricing" class="relative bg-brand-dark-deep py-20 px-6 overflow-hidden scroll-mt-8">
    <div class="absolute top-[-200px] left-[-100px] w-[600px] h-[600px] rounded-full bg-[radial-gradient(circle,rgba(0,146,202,0.1)_0%,transparent_65%)] pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-[-150px] right-[-80px] w-[400px] h-[400px] rounded-full bg-[radial-gradient(circle,rgba(0,146,202,0.06)_0%,transparent_65%)] pointer-events-none"></div>

    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/10 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 mb-4">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M20.25 6.375c0 2.278-3.694 4.125-8.25 4.125S3.75 8.653 3.75 6.375m16.5 0c0-2.278-3.694-4.125-8.25-4.125S3.75 4.097 3.75 6.375m16.5 0v11.25c0 2.278-3.694 4.125-8.25 4.125s-8.25-1.847-8.25-4.125V6.375m16.5 0v3.75m-16.5-3.75v3.75m16.5 0v3.75C20.25 16.153 16.556 18 12 18s-8.25-1.847-8.25-4.125v-3.75m16.5 0c0 2.278-3.694 4.125-8.25 4.125s-8.25-1.847-8.25-4.125" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[2px] text-white/70">Data Lake™</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-white tracking-tight mb-3">Access Transparency Data Directly</h2>
        <p class="text-base text-white/55 max-w-lg mx-auto">Deliver the most complete price transparency data directly into your own infrastructure.</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/40 mt-4">
          <span class="mr-2">Available on</span>
          {['Snowflake', 'Databricks', 'AWS', 'GCP', 'Azure', 'All major cloud data platforms'].map((platform, i) => (
            <>
              <span class="font-semibold text-white/70">{platform}</span>
              {i < 5 && <span class="mx-1.5 text-white/20">·</span>}
            </>
          ))}
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
        <!-- Header row -->
        <div class="hidden sm:grid grid-cols-[1fr_auto_auto] items-center gap-4 px-8 py-4 bg-white/5 border-b border-white/10">
          <span class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[1.5px] text-white/40">Price Transparency Algorithm (PTA)</span>
          <span class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[1.5px] text-white/40 text-right w-32">Starting At</span>
          <span class="w-32"></span>
        </div>

        {[
          { tier: 'Tier 1', name: 'Up to 100 Billing Codes', desc: 'Nationwide coverage', price: '75', label: 'K/yr', cta: 'Get Started', ctaStyle: 'bg-white hover:bg-slate-100 text-brand-dark shadow-[0_4px_16px_rgba(255,255,255,0.1)]', link: { text: 'View PTA documentation', href: 'https://docs.payerset.com/data-lake/payerset-price-transparency-algorithm' } },
          { tier: 'Tier 2', name: 'Up to 500 Billing Codes', desc: 'Nationwide coverage', price: '150', label: 'K/yr', cta: 'Get Started', ctaStyle: 'bg-white hover:bg-slate-100 text-brand-dark shadow-[0_4px_16px_rgba(255,255,255,0.1)]', link: null },
          { tier: 'Tier 3', name: 'All Billing Codes', desc: 'Complete nationwide coverage', price: '288', label: 'K/yr', cta: 'Get Started', ctaStyle: 'bg-white hover:bg-slate-100 text-brand-dark shadow-[0_4px_16px_rgba(255,255,255,0.1)]', link: null },
        ].map(({ tier, name, desc, price, label, cta, ctaStyle, link }, i) => (
          <div class:list={[
            "sm:grid grid-cols-[1fr_auto_auto] items-center gap-4 px-8 py-5 transition-colors hover:bg-white/[0.03]",
            i < 2 ? "border-b border-white/10" : "",
          ]}>
            <div class="mb-3 sm:mb-0">
              <p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[2px] text-white/40 mb-0.5">{tier}</p>
              <p class="text-lg font-bold text-white leading-tight">{name}</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-white/50">{desc}</p>
              {link && (
                <a href={link.href} class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs font-medium text-brand-primary hover:text-brand-primary-hover mt-1">
                  {link.text} <span class="text-[10px]">↗</span>
                </a>
              )}
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-baseline font-heading w-32 justify-end mb-3 sm:mb-0">
              <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-white self-start pt-1">$</span>
              <span class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-white leading-none tracking-tight">{price}</span>
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-white/50 ml-0.5">{label}</span>
            </div>
            <a href="/get-started" class:list={["block w-32 text-center px-4 py-3 rounded-lg text-sm font-semibold transition-colors", ctaStyle]}>
              {cta}
            </a>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <!-- Employer plans callout -->
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mt-4 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl px-8 py-5">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M11.25 11.25l.041-.02a.75.75 0 011.063.852l-.708 2.836a.75.75 0 001.063.853l.041-.021M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0zm-9-3.75h.008v.008H12V8.25z" />
          </svg>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/60">
            All tiers above include commercial plans and Type 2 NPI data. Need employer-level plans, individual (Type 1) NPI coverage, or a package that doesn't quite fit the tiers above? <a href="/get-started" class="text-brand-primary hover:text-brand-primary-lighter underline underline-offset-2">Contact us</a> and we'll build a custom package for you.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-center text-xs text-white/30 mt-4">All prices billed annually. Pricing scoped to your use case.</p>

      <!-- Enterprise Data Syndication -->
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mt-10 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-primary/10 to-brand-primary/5 border border-brand-primary/20 rounded-xl p-8">
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between gap-6">
          <div>
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-brand-primary/15 rounded-full px-3 py-1 mb-3">
              <span class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[2px] text-brand-primary">Enterprise</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Enterprise Data Syndication</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/55 max-w-md">Full-scale access to the complete Payerset data asset — every billing code, every geography, Type 1 and Type 2 NPIs, employer plans and commercial.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/get-started" class="shrink-0 inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 rounded-lg text-sm font-semibold bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/15 text-white border border-white/20 transition-colors">
            Contact Us
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ── EVERY DATA LAKE PLAN INCLUDES ── -->
      <div class="mt-16">
        <div class="text-center mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-white tracking-tight">Every Data Lake Plan Includes</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
          {[
            {
              title: 'Every Payer & Hospital MRF',
              desc: '100% of published machine-readable files ingested, enriched, and standardized. No subsets, no cherry-picking.',
              icon: `<path d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/>`,
            },
            {
              title: 'Historical Trending',
              desc: 'Full historical data for every payer and hospital dataset. Track reimbursement movement over time.',
              icon: `<path d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"/>`,
            },
            {
              title: 'Quarterly Refreshes',
              desc: 'Full dataset audit and refresh every quarter. Always current with the latest payer structures and CMS requirements.',
              icon: `<path d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15"/>`,
            },
            {
              title: 'Data Delivery',
              desc: 'Get your data however you need it. REST API, scheduled extracts to your infrastructure, or cloud data shares.',
